{"tid":689840,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"8日7夜第一次東京行程求評","createTime":"2018-06-04T11:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T11:14:08.000Z","uid":45029,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8ffcae2ce716a1b1feb5919ea4b76e2c777c2e48","tid":689840,"uid":45029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:13:20.000Z","msg":"6月中同女朋友第一次去東京<br />\n地方行程都係睇旅遊書，上網搵，求評價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 機場&mdash;池袋<br />\n應該成5點先到機場，住池袋，打算食個飯行一陣就返民宿<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: 三鷹美術館&mdash;未有計劃<br />\n出發去睇宮崎駿美術館，預睇到5、6點，之後未有行程<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: 池袋<br />\n係池袋行街，主要行J-world同sunshine city<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 淺草&mdash;上野&mdash;秋葉原<br />\n一早出發去雷門、淺草寺打卡，之後考慮緊去唔去上野，聽朋友講上野可以行到去秋葉原，沿途有商店街，最後秋葉原睇動漫<br />\n<br />\nDay 5: 築地&mdash;暫定一番街<br />\n一早去築地，之後暫定一番家<br />\n<br />\nDay 6: 迪士尼<br />\n<br />\nDay 7: 暫定台場<br />\n行商場同海濱公園<br />\n<br />\nDay 8: 夜晚8點機<br />\n睇下有咩地方最後衝刺<br />\n<br />\n除左上面仲有無好地方推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910dc96cd1ebc8b99bbc32b3e53c4cfa0b535ca4","tid":689840,"uid":16376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:16:30.000Z","msg":"覺得第七同第八日可以一齊"},{"pid":"385f86e75862b0872d2c8fd5979e53cf251b7f38","tid":689840,"uid":21696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:16:39.000Z","msg":"原宿新宿得閒都可以逛吓"},{"pid":"9baa7d1b7d577045b924b6d012a15acfa2e20bc3","tid":689840,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:18:18.000Z","msg":"留名，我嚟緊月尾都係咁。想問大家有冇配過眼鏡"},{"pid":"07df6515af58c67208e378c4f8722da4258d041d","tid":689840,"uid":30865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/192255_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F192255_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=46733784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎緊既7日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9631a1e1d2e09583dff658434732ba8e4f1d6046","tid":689840,"uid":89909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"岩岩上個月去完，行程如下：<br />\nDay 1: 7:30pm落機，返新宿安頓食飯<br />\nDay 2: 去富士山睇芝櫻，然後直落伊豆住溫泉酒店<br />\nDay 3: 伊豆一日遊 (大室山+伊豆八境其中幾個，夜晚jr返新宿<br />\nDay 4: 築地、淺草、上野行街<br />\nDay 5: 木更津outlet<br />\nDay 6: 鎌倉、江之島一日遊<br />\nDay 7: 明治神宮、東京皇宮、東京車站內外附近、芝公園、東京鐵塔<br />\nDay 8: 川越一日遊<br />\nDay 9: 東京都廳、新宿車站附近藥庄掃貨、2點去機場<br />\n<br />\n註：基本上全程住新宿"},{"pid":"dd8a4a778b415f1badde6565ded3d7c6f3e8c8d6","tid":689840,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:50:46.000Z","msg":"Day 2 三鷹撲左飛未? 好快滿<br />\n無飛可以改去井之頭公園+動物園<br />\n夜晚吉祥寺都有野食有街行<br />\n<br />\n可以考慮下遠小小，川越，高尾山，青梅。<br />\n或市內新宿，原宿，甚至上野的博物館群"},{"pid":"b0f87a931b22417acf5727477e0eb53fa2f56123","tid":689840,"uid":49182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:27:30.000Z","msg":"我都6月中去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7dc0bbc780660f1d5dcf28169901cd4ad39926","tid":689840,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07df6515af58c67208e378c4f8722da4258d041d","tid":689840,"uid":30865,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T11:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/04/192255_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F04%2F192255_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=46733784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黎緊既7日行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T12:32:08.000Z","msg":"你原宿嗰日咁密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去台場剩係影個自由神像彩虹橋就走？<img sr